description:
Darkness Radio investigates a story so frightening you may have trouble sleeping when you hear it, Hanover Haunting - The DeAnna Simpson Story with DeAnna Simpson and Joni Mayhan.

Wrong place, wrong time with the right person working as a catalyst for a true paranormal nightmare. This is DeAnna Simpsons story.

Follow here for more info: https://bit.ly/39c35oI

To follow along with changes going on with the show, go to www.darknessradio.com
